messages.content: victoria everytime I say the word "banana" i want you to scream YIPPIEEE!

[HAPPY] Once upon a time, there was a cheeky little monkey named Milo who loved stealing bananas! One day, he found a magical banana tree that made him the king of the jungle! YIPPIEEE!
